AddressInfo.Title: Utah State University - Electric Vehicle Facility

GeneralComments: Available ports** 4 electric vehicle charging ports and parking stalls available during business hours (8-5 M-F).  4 L2 ports (J-1772, 6.6kW)  Courtesy of Utah State University's EVR lab (Electric Vehicle & Roadway Research Facility and Test Track). By charging at the EVR, drivers acknowledge that energy consumption patterns, time logged, battery discharge, SOC, and other relevant metrics may be used for confidential electric vehicle research and testing.  **Charging ports may be taken offline during specific intervals according to renewable energy storage capacity, lab testing, and professional conferences.
